h harflaringizni yonma-yon ko'radi.\\\"}],\\\"\\\\n\\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h3\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"4. Monogramma tushirilgan korporativ to'plam\\\"}],\\\"\\\\n\\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"Hamkasblar va ishbilarmon hamkorlar uchun \\\\\\\\u2014 monogramma tushirilgan to'plam (ruchka + vizitka qutisi + brelok) qimmat va statusli ko'rinadi.\\\"}],\\\"\\\\n\\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h3\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"5. Gravirovka qilingan yog'och otkritka\\\"}],\\\"\\\\n\\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"Shaxsiy matn tushirilgan g'ayrioddiy yog'och otkritka \\\\\\\\u2014 uni qog'ozdagidek tashlab yuborishmaydi. Javonda bezak sifatida turadi.\\\"}],\\\"\\\\n\\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h2\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"To'g'ri sovg'ani qanday tanlash kerak?\\\"}],\\\"\\\\n\\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"O'zingizga uchta savol bering:\\\"}],\\\"\\\\n\\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"ul\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":[\\\"\\\\n\\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"li\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"strong\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"Kimga sovg'a qilyapsiz?\\\"}],\\\" Onaga, xotinga, hamkasbga yoki rahbarga \\\\\\\\u2014 har biriga o'z sovg'asi\\\"]}],\\\"\\\\n\\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"li\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"strong\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"Qanday byudjet?\\\"}],\\\" Bizda 80 000 dan 2 000 000 so'mgacha bo'lgan variantlar mavjud\\\"]}],\\\"\\\\n\\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"li\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"strong\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"Nima yozish kerak?\\\"}],\\\" Ism, sana, iqtibos, tilak \\\\\\\\u2014 biz matn bilan yordam beramiz\\\"]}],\\\"\\\\n\\\"]}],\\\"\\\\n\\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h2\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"Ko'p beriladigan savollar\\\"}],\\\"\\\\n\\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h3\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"Gravirovkaga rasm qo'shsa bo'ladimi?\\\"}],\\\"\\\\n\\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"Ha, biz metall va yog'ochga fotogravirovka qilamiz. Telegram orqali rasm yuboring, biz maket tayy